Benefits of using the device for the patient
Patient benefits

Not only are devices vital for providing staff with a more efficient data access point.  The benefits are endless for the patient too. From improving patient feedback with bed side access to devices for entertainment, to uses in consultations, self management apps, and connecting the patient to relatives and family.
Click to see Microsoft's vision of how devices can help, when the human touch is not possible.
Access your data and information from virtually anywhere
Access data anywhere

When working from a range of devices all running on a Windows platform, the possibilities to access your desktop and key information is endless.  Nurses and Clinicians are now able to access and complete administration, look at notes, and fill in forms at the bed side.
